channel.title: Unhandled packet
channel.description:
When I drop an item and above the "take" option there are two "[b]..[/b] and when I click on them it says this.
[code]Unhandled packet [23, InterFaceId: 48269, size=6] ]0D 57 35 18 0C 40[
Action Button: 188189[/code]
I know partly what it means but knowing that how would I fix that annoying option with two dots??
